Job Description:
- Design and develop test cases based on product requirement documents; perform functional testing, regression testing, compatibility testing, etc.;
- Responsible for functional and performance testing across Web, Mobile App, and Miniapp platforms; candidates with experience in testing e-commerce platforms, especially online shopping systems, will be preferred;
- Follow up on customer feedback by reproducing issues, logging and tracking defects, and collaborating with relevant teams to drive resolution and ensure product quality and customer satisfaction;
- Prepare and maintain related test documentation, including test plans, test reports, and defect logs; build and manage test data as needed.

Job Requirements:
- Bachelor’s degree or above in Computer Science or a related field, with 2+ years of experience in software testing;
